    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      495.91,
      544.14,
      507.91
    ],
    "text": "However, the Supreme Court in Blanka Diamonds (Pvt) Ltd v. Van Els [(2004) 3 Sri.L.R. 314] held",
